definition.value: An  azaphilone  that is 6H-furo[2,3-h]isochromene-6,8(6aH)-dione substituted by a chloro group at position 5, a 3-hydroxy-2-methylbutanoyl group at position 9, a methyl group at position 6a and a 3-methylpent-1-en-1yl group at position 3. Isolated from Chaetomium globosum, it exhibits natifungal activity against plant pathogenic fungi.
An organic heterotetracyclic compound with formula C23H27ClO6 isolated from Chaetomium globosum. It exhibits antifungal activity against plant pathogenic fungi.
